3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep neural networks for feature extraction and classification. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new topological metric space determined by the deep network. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image segmentation and saliency detection, which are important topics in multimedia research.
